-stallion-rm-bts@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/megan-thee-stallion-rm-bts@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/megan-thee-stallion-rm-bts@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/megan-thee-stallion-rm-bts@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>宣布了她的新单曲“Neva Play”，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行</a>男孩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rm">RM</a>合作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/megan-thee-stallion-london-the-o2-live-review-setlist-photos-3776033">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 伦敦现场演出：为里程碑式的巡演充满自信</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚，这位“Mamushi”说唱歌手在社交媒体上正式宣布了“Neva Play”，该歌曲<a href="https://x.com/theestallion/status/1829188506305929573" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在周末首次被调侃</a>。现在，已确认 BTS 明星 RM 将与她一起参与新曲目，该曲目将于本周五（9 月 6 日）发布。</p><p> Megan Thee Stallion 如此评价 RM 和这首歌：“这是我听过的最喜欢的 RM 诗句之一！我以前从未听过他用这种风格说唱。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_YPe5gPblE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" backgro